        {
            "title": "海關破大埔可卡因製毒工場 34歲無業男拒捕傷兩關員 被控3罪明提堂",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/2ce3da012136962490938ed9c9d862e9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250418/_2025041818530548071.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>海關昨日（17日）於大埔進行反毒品行動，其間截查一名可疑男子，並在其斜孭袋內搜出570克霹靂可卡因，隨即上前拘捕。人員押送該名男子到一村屋單位搜查，再檢獲560克疑可卡因、約30克疑霹靂可卡因，以及一批製毒及毒品包裝工具，市值約120萬元。\n\n</p>\n<p>被捕男子34歲，報稱無業，已被控一項販賣危險藥物罪、一項製造危險藥物罪、一項抗拒海關人員罪，案件將於明日（19日）在屯門裁判法院提堂。\n\n</p>\n<p>海關指被捕男子沒有黑幫背景，租用涉事村屋單位作製毒工場約兩個月，由包裝到出貨全部一人負責「一腳踢」，而毒品主要供應大埔及北區市場。消息指，男子曾拒捕導致兩名關員受傷。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203138/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"被捕男子報稱無業。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0b7bd33403a382fda4204e4067d0e521/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250418_181614909_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        被捕男子報稱無業。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203131/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關檢獲一批製毒及毒品包裝工具。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/21249c46d1d6b6092efa31d2ee0f7f2c/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250418_181650292_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關檢獲一批製毒及毒品包裝工具。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203132/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關檢獲一批可卡因及霹靂可卡因。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0f4347995b379911a2c9c088a22a8edb/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250418_181650292_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關檢獲一批可卡因及霹靂可卡因。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203133/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關檢獲一批可卡因及霹靂可卡因，市值約120萬元。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/64360bc4b39a4b96b374290c1dbd70db/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250418_181650292_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關檢獲一批可卡因及霹靂可卡因，市值約120萬元。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203134/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關檢獲一批製毒及毒品包裝工具。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d0ce15d6b9d51dbe170a9ee90b7e2d70/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250418_181650292_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關檢獲一批製毒及毒品包裝工具。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203135/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關檢獲一批可卡因及霹靂可卡因，市值約120萬元。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/74de319966b99ee2a0a3b1a42589d593/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250418_181650292_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關檢獲一批可卡因及霹靂可卡因，市值約120萬元。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203136/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關檢獲一批製毒及毒品包裝工具。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c4b8830505f87f3e41a731f2544a127d/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250418_181650292.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關檢獲一批製毒及毒品包裝工具。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203137/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關指被捕男子曾拒捕，導致兩名關員擦傷。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6a388904f1ea0cd437f761a37bd1730c/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250418_181604630_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關指被捕男子曾拒捕，導致兩名關員擦傷。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
